                <article class="editor"><h2 class="title" style="text-align: left;"><span style="font-size: 19px;"><strong>Inspired to flourish, innovate and be responsible global citizens.</strong></span></h2>
<p>&nbsp;</p>
<p class="rounded_title bg-colour1"><a href="https://abacus.esf.edu.hk/en/about_us/what_we_stand_for/" target="_blank" rel="noopener"><span style="color: #ffffff;">Discover Our Vision</span></a></p></article>
            </div>
