                <article class="editor"><h2 class="title"><span style="font-size: 19px;"><strong><img class="round-border" src="https://abacus.esf.edu.hk/upload/page/35/self/6757b766919b9.jpg" alt="" width="459" height="344" /></strong></span></h2>
<h2 class="title">&nbsp;</h2>
<h2 class="title"><span style="font-size: 19px;"><strong>Inspired to flourish, innovate and be responsible global citizens.</strong></span></h2>
<p>&nbsp;</p>
<p class="rounded_title bg-colour1"><a href="https://abacus.esf.edu.hk/en/about_us/what_we_stand_for/"><span style="color: #ffffff;">Discover Our Vision</span></a></p></article>
            </div>
            </div>
</section>
<section id="section2">
    <div class="container">
        <div class="section-title">
            <h2 class="colour2">What can Abacus offer your family?</h2>
            <span class="bg-colour1"></span>
        </div>
    </div>
    <div class="wrapper bg-colour2">
        <div class="container">
            <ul>
                                    <li>
                        <div class="bg-colour3">
                                                            <img src="/cache/img/c0db9eac58f99ac59f83b82cc6c871ee.png" alt="SIS offers icon-6" loading="lazy" width="270" height="270" />                             
                            <h3 class="colour1">ESF Network</h3>
                            <div class="overlay bg-colour1">
                                <p>As part of the English Schools Foundation(ESF), our students are supported by the largest English-medium international school organisation in Hong Kong, providing them the resources and opportunities not found outside of ESF Schools.</p>
                                                                    <a  href="https://abacus.esf.edu.hk/en/about_us/ESF_family/">
                                        <span>Find out more</span>
                                    </a>
                                                            </div>
                        </div>
                    </li>
                                    <li>
                        <div class="bg-colour3">
                                                            <img src="/cache/img/e7839d46948b1c6b9b494eadf9f57c5b.png" alt="World-class Education" loading="lazy" width="270" height="270" />                             
                            <h3 class="colour1">World-Class Education</h3>
                            <div class="overlay bg-colour1">
                                <p>Our kindergarten offers a high-quality International Baccalaureate Primary Years Programme curriculum delivered by experienced, quality teachers.</p>
                                                                    <a  href="https://abacus.esf.edu.hk/en/outstanding_education/curriculum/">
                                        <span>Find out more</span>
                                    </a>
                                                            </div>
                        </div>
                    </li>
                                    <li>
                        <div class="bg-colour3">
                                                            <img src="/cache/img/aef7d644a0bf3394fb3af0cc9a0ca1b0.png" alt="Real-world Experience" loading="lazy" width="270" height="270" />                             
                            <h3 class="colour1">Inclusive Nurturing Staff</h3>
                            <div class="overlay bg-colour1">
                                <p>We celebrate diversity and create an inclusive, welcoming environment where every child feels valued and can flourish.</p>
                                                                    <a  href="https://abacus.esf.edu.hk/en/outstanding_education/student_support_Wellbeing/">
                                        <span>Find out more</span>
                                    </a>
                                                            </div>
                        </div>
                    </li>
                                    <li>
                        <div class="bg-colour3">
                                                            <img src="/cache/img/575626fef0cfbe229bb7ce02c55e4804.png" alt="Well-rounded Education (1)" loading="lazy" width="270" height="270" />                             
                            <h3 class="colour1">Exciting Learning</h3>
                            <div class="overlay bg-colour1">
                                <p>Our engaging approach to learning inspires creativity and curiosity and develops attitudes such as resilience and independence.</p>
                                                                    <a  href="https://abacus.esf.edu.hk/en/outstanding_education/our_approach/">
                                        <span>Find out more</span>
                                    </a>
                                                            </div>
                        </div>
                    </li>
                                    <li>
                        <div class="bg-colour3">
                                                            <img src="/cache/img/afaca7733309c082a1ab23aea54a52ed.png" alt="Comprehensive Student Support" loading="lazy" width="270" height="270" />                             
                            <h3 class="colour1">Engaging Learning Environment</h3>
                            <div class="overlay bg-colour1">
                                <p>A natural and engaging environment to inspire and nurture young learners.</p>
                                                                    <a  href="https://abacus.esf.edu.hk/en/outstanding_experiences/educational_visits_events/">
                                        <span>Find out more</span>
                                    </a>
                                                            </div>
                        </div>
                    </li>
                                    <li>
                        <div class="bg-colour3">
                                                            <img src="/cache/img/2891b58f1df5e70d649bedc171ecbb97.png" alt="Strong School-Family Connection" loading="lazy" width="270" height="270" />                             
                            <h3 class="colour1">Strong Community</h3>
                            <div class="overlay bg-colour1">
                                <p>Our supportive and inclusive community is fostered through collaborative partnerships between parents, staff, and children.</p>
                                                                    <a  href="https://abacus.esf.edu.hk/en/outstanding_people/parent_partnerships/">
                                        <span>Find out more</span>
                                    </a>
                                                            </div>
                        </div>
                    </li>
                            </ul>
        </div>
    </div>
    <script type="text/javascript">
        $(window).load(function() {
            $('h3', '#section2').each(function() {
                let img = $(this).parent().children('img');
                if(img.length) {
                    $(this).css('top', img.offset().top + img.height() + 25 - $(this).parent().offset().top);
                }
            });
        });
    </script>
</section>
<section id="section3">
    <img src="/cache/img/2297d1c9c3c28492a27eb30c2e01eae2.jpg" alt="abacus_kindy_4109" loading="lazy" width="1722" height="1294" />    <div class="wrapper">
        <div class="section-title-container">
            <div class="section-title">
                <h2 class="colour2">Outstanding Education</h2>
                <span class="bg-colour1"></span>
            </div>
        </div>
        <div class="tabs">
                            <button class="tab current" data-id="1"></button>
                    </div>
                            <div class="tab-content current" data-id="1">
                                <article class="editor"><p><span style="font-weight: 400;">Abacus is an IB World School. Teachers skillfully use the IB Primary Years Programme to engage our learners in a challenging and meaningful curriculum. Through play, the children learn to be independent thinkers and successful collaborators. The environment at Abacus is language-rich for the children in both our Bilingual and English classrooms.&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;</span></p></article>
                                    <a href="https://abacus.esf.edu.hk/en/outstanding_education/">
                        <span>Learn more</span>
                    </a>
                            </div>
                <script type="text/javascript">
            $(document).ready(function() {
                $('.select .select-container div:nth-child(' + ($('.tab.current', '#section3').index() + 1) + ')', '#section3').hide();

                $('.tab', '#section3').click(function() {
                    $('.tab, .tab-content', '#section3').removeClass('current');
                    $(this).addClass('current');
                    $('.tab-content[data-id=' + $(this).data('id') + ']', '#section3').addClass('current');
                    $('select', '#section3').val($(this).data('id')).selectbox('refresh');
                    $('.select .select-container div', '#section3').show();
                    $('.select .select-container div:nth-child(' + ($('.tab.current', '#section3').index() + 1) + ')', '#section3').hide();
                });

                $('.tab-select', '#section3').change(function() {
                    $('.tab, .tab-content', '#section3').removeClass('current');
                    $('.tab[data-id=' + $(this).val() + ']').addClass('current');
                    $('.tab-content[data-id=' + $(this).val() + ']', '#section3').addClass('current');
                    $('.select .select-container div', '#section3').show();
                    $('.select .select-container div:nth-child(' + ($('.tab.current', '#section3').index() + 1) + ')', '#section3').hide();
                });
            });
        </script>
    </div>
</section>
