                        </div>
                                    </div>
                            <div class="tab-content" data-id="2">
                                            <div class="record-slider">
                            <div class="slider-container">
                                                                    <div class="record-item">
                                        <div class="left">
                                            <div class="thumbnail bg-colour1">
                                                <span></span>
                                                <img src="/cache/img/433a1aa07e21182aebbdadbbacb7aa5d.jpg" alt="" loading="lazy" width="548" height="548" />                                            </div>
                                                                                            <div class="slider-pager">
                                                    <button class="prev"></button>
                                                    <span>1 / 5</span>
                                                    <button class="next"></button>
                                                </div>
                                                                                    </div>
                                        <div class="right">
                                            <article>
                                                                                                    <div class="content">
                                                        <p class="description">One of the best things about Abacus is the community it has built. As a family, we are proud to tell others that our children attend the school as it's well known that children who go through Abacus and the ESF system as a whole are really wonderful, caring and bright. The themes around how to structure learning throughout the school year are really well thought out, especially for the age that Abacus looks after. Learning through play is so important for children especially in Hong Kong and this generation when parents can fall down the slippery slope of over-scheduling. I know that if my children did nothing else outside of school they would be incredibly fulfilled because of the learning environment built by Abacus.</p>
                                                        <button class="view-more">
                                                            <span>View More</span>
                                                        </button>
                                                        <p class="content">One of the best things about Abacus is the community it has built. As a family, we are proud to tell others that our children attend the school as it's well known that children who go through Abacus and the ESF system as a whole are really wonderful, caring and bright. The themes around how to structure learning throughout the school year are really well thought out, especially for the age that Abacus looks after. Learning through play is so important for children especially in Hong Kong and this generation when parents can fall down the slippery slope of over-scheduling. I know that if my children did nothing else outside of school they would be incredibly fulfilled because of the learning environment built by Abacus.</p>
                                                        <button class="view-less">
                                                            <span>View Less</span>
                                                        </button>
                                                    </div>
                                                                                            </article>
                                                                                            <div class="title">
                                                    <span></span>
                                                    <h3>Anonymous - School Stakeholder Survey 2024</h3>
                                                </div>
                                                                                    </div>
                                    </div>
                                                                    <div class="record-item">
                                        <div class="left">
                                            <div class="thumbnail bg-colour1">
                                                <span></span>
                                                <img src="/cache/img/433a1aa07e21182aebbdadbbacb7aa5d.jpg" alt="" loading="lazy" width="548" height="548" />                                            </div>
                                                                                            <div class="slider-pager">
                                                    <button class="prev"></button>
                                                    <span>2 / 5</span>
                                                    <button class="next"></button>
                                                </div>
                                                                                    </div>
                                        <div class="right">
                                            <article>
                                                                                                    <div class="content">
                                                        <p class="description">Abacus is a great school, my child loves being at school and is really well cared for by staff. We love the school and especially the outdoor area. Great leadership and great teachers.</p>
                                                        <button class="view-more">
                                                            <span>View More</span>
                                                        </button>
                                                        <p class="content">Abacus is a great school, my child loves being at school and is really well cared for by staff. We love the school and especially the outdoor area. Great leadership and great teachers.</p>
                                                        <button class="view-less">
                                                            <span>View Less</span>
                                                        </button>
                                                    </div>
                                                                                            </article>
                                                                                            <div class="title">
                                                    <span></span>
                                                    <h3>Anonymous - School Stakeholder Survey 2024</h3>
                                                </div>
                                                                                    </div>
                                    </div>
                                                                    <div class="record-item">
                                        <div class="left">
                                            <div class="thumbnail bg-colour1">
                                                <span></span>
                                                <img src="/cache/img/f6dfb6d8f15055f3656524c508f895f2.jpg" alt="Pilar" loading="lazy" width="548" height="548" />                                            </div>
                                                                                            <div class="slider-pager">
                                                    <button class="prev"></button>
                                                    <span>3 / 5</span>
                                                    <button class="next"></button>
                                                </div>
                                                                                    </div>
                                        <div class="right">
                                            <article>
                                                                                                    <div class="content">
                                                        <p class="description">Before applying to Abacus we were told what a beautiful community it was, but it was not until our son joined the school that we could quite grasp the extent of this community and the supportive, nurturing, inclusive nature that it harbours. I have not experienced this elsewhere in Hong Kong and unquestionably recommend Abacus</p>
                                                        <button class="view-more">
                                                            <span>View More</span>
                                                        </button>
                                                        <p class="content">Before applying to Abacus we were told what a beautiful community it was, but it was not until our son joined the school that we could quite grasp the extent of this community and the supportive, nurturing, inclusive nature that it harbours. I have not experienced this elsewhere in Hong Kong and unquestionably recommend Abacus</p>
                                                        <button class="view-less">
                                                            <span>View Less</span>
                                                        </button>
                                                    </div>
                                                                                            </article>
                                                                                            <div class="title">
                                                    <span></span>
                                                    <h3>Pilar Morais</h3>
                                                </div>
                                                                                    </div>
                                    </div>
                                                                    <div class="record-item">
                                        <div class="left">
                                            <div class="thumbnail bg-colour1">
                                                <span></span>
                                                <img src="/cache/img/433a1aa07e21182aebbdadbbacb7aa5d.jpg" alt="" loading="lazy" width="548" height="548" />                                            </div>
                                                                                            <div class="slider-pager">
                                                    <button class="prev"></button>
                                                    <span>4 / 5</span>
                                                    <button class="next"></button>
                                                </div>
                                                                                    </div>
                                        <div class="right">
                                            <article>
                                                                                                    <div class="content">
                                                        <p class="description">The learning environment at ESF abacus is optimal for all young children. It’s been almost a year since my daughter joined the school and I see immense change in her independence and confidence.The curriculum and teaching methods are very well designed as they embrace a child for learning and development. Teachers are amazing and they take good care of every student. They are child centred and make coming to school so much fun.There is never a dull moment at school with all the fun activities and messy play. We recommend ESF Abacus Kindergarten to everyone!</p>
                                                        <button class="view-more">
                                                            <span>View More</span>
                                                        </button>
                                                        <p class="content">The learning environment at ESF abacus is optimal for all young children. It’s been almost a year since my daughter joined the school and I see immense change in her independence and confidence.The curriculum and teaching methods are very well designed as they embrace a child for learning and development. Teachers are amazing and they take good care of every student. They are child centred and make coming to school so much fun.There is never a dull moment at school with all the fun activities and messy play. We recommend ESF Abacus Kindergarten to everyone!</p>
                                                        <button class="view-less">
                                                            <span>View Less</span>
                                                        </button>
                                                    </div>
                                                                                            </article>
