                                        <div class="right">
                                            <article>
                                                                                                    <div class="content">
                                                        <p class="description">Abacus is a fantastic school that offers a wonderfully nurturing and engaging learning environment for our students. Staff are supportive and friendly, I feel supported, valued and heard by Senior Leadership. I can't wait for my son to be joining Abacus this coming August, I know it will offer him a fantastic start to his school journey. I genuinely feel lucky every day to be a part of our learning community.</p>
                                                        <button class="view-more">
                                                            <span>View More</span>
                                                        </button>
                                                        <p class="content">Abacus is a fantastic school that offers a wonderfully nurturing and engaging learning environment for our students. Staff are supportive and friendly, I feel supported, valued and heard by Senior Leadership. I can't wait for my son to be joining Abacus this coming August, I know it will offer him a fantastic start to his school journey. I genuinely feel lucky every day to be a part of our learning community.</p>
