                                        <div class="right">
                                            <article>
                                                                                                    <div class="content">
                                                        <p class="description">Staff and Parents work like a team here, transparency is so beautifully handled, staff seems to genuinely care for each and every child's and colleague's well-being, so much room to make mistakes and learn from them in order to perform better.  Growth mindset and the effort that's put in here by the leadership to take every individual to their maximum potential is exceptional.</p>
                                                        <button class="view-more">
                                                            <span>View More</span>
                                                        </button>
                                                        <p class="content">Staff and Parents work like a team here, transparency is so beautifully handled, staff seems to genuinely care for each and every child's and colleague's well-being, so much room to make mistakes and learn from them in order to perform better.  Growth mindset and the effort that's put in here by the leadership to take every individual to their maximum potential is exceptional.</p>
